---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const updated = '2026-03-11';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure — Glow Intel"
  description="Affiliate and sponsorship disclosure for Glow Intel, in compliance with FTC guidelines."
>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="text-sm mb-10" style="color: var(--text-muted);">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <div class="prose">
        <h2>FTC compliance</h2>
        <p>In compliance with the Federal Trade Commission (FTC) guidelines, Glow Intel discloses any material connections between this site and any products or brands mentioned.</p>

        <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
        <p>Some links on Glow Intel may be affiliate links. This means if you click through and make a purchase, we may receive a small commission at no additional cost to you. Affiliate relationships do not influence editorial opinions — products are recommended based on their merit, not on commission rates.</p>
        <p>Posts that contain affiliate links are labeled accordingly.</p>

        <h2>Sponsored content</h2>
        <p>If Glow Intel ever publishes sponsored content or receives products for review, it will be clearly disclosed at the top of that post. Sponsored posts represent the honest opinion of the author — we do not publish positive reviews in exchange for compensation.</p>

        <h2>Free products</h2>
        <p>If a product was received for free for review purposes, this will be noted in the post. Free products do not guarantee a positive review.</p>

        <h2>Questions</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about a specific post or partnership, you can reach out via the <a href="/about">About page</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
